      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 mated to a longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits crisp throttle response via its eight individual throttle bodies, with the rod bearings and throttle actuators already addressed as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains taut, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry that provides exceptional lateral grip. Power is delivered to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The braking system features cross-drilled rotors with high thermal capacity, showing minimal glazing. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the mechanical synchronicity and drivetrain integrity are characteristic of a well-sorted enthusiast vehicle.",
